  Stable on alpha and ppc

  24 Jun 2004; Mamoru KOMACHI <usata@gentoo.org> ruby-gconf2-0.8.1.ebuild,
  ruby-gconf2-0.9.1.ebuild:
  Stable on x86

  17 Apr 2004; David Holm <dholm@gentoo.org> ruby-gconf2-0.9.1.ebuild:
  Added to ~ppc.

  12 Apr 2004; Mamoru KOMACHI <usata@gentoo.org> ruby-gconf2-0.5.0.ebuild,
  ruby-gconf2-0.8.1.ebuild, ruby-gconf2-0.9.1.ebuild:
  Removed 0.5.0. Added ruby.eclass support.

*ruby-gconf2-0.9.1 (18 Mar 2004)

  18 Mar 2004; Aron Griffis <agriffis@gentoo.org> ruby-gconf2-0.8.0.ebuild,
